+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: Node.js 24
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- focused: `ref={scenario}; file="${ref%:*}"; name="${ref##*:}"; npx cucumber-js "$file" --name "$name" --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- coverage: `npx c8 --reporter=text-summary --reporter=json-summary --reports-dir=coverage npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage-json:features/_step_usage.json --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- plank-inventory: `rg -n --no-heading '@planks(?:-provisional)?\(' src`
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: none
+- conformance: none
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: @logic runs no external services and uses no credentials
+- weather: coverage/_weather.json
+- runrecord: coverage/_runrecord.jsonl
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: latest-stable
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber
+- dependency: c8
+- dependency: jsdoc
+- dependency: knip
+- dependency: @biomejs/biome
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
