+Feature: Methodology conformance
+
+  Methodology checks assert the project's own method rather than product
+  behaviour. They live in the binding layer only when Captain promotes
+  them; until then the `@captain` tag keeps them out of QM and every
+  derived verification command.
+
+  Rule: The implementation directories are listed in RIGGING.md under
+  `## Directories` as `implementation`. The repository root is the
+  project root for all path resolution.
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Watchbill shape conforms when no watchbill is present
+    Given the project has no watchbill.json at the repository root
+    When the watchbill shape check runs
+    Then the check passes because an absent watchbill is the deck at rest
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Perturbation quiescence holds on a green tree
+    Given a green verification tree with no live perturbation
+    When the perturbation quiescence check runs
+    Then no PERTURBATION token is present in the implementation directories
